name: Meet me in the void - Encounter
description:
Meet me in the void - Encounter, 2022, video, 15s
With the "Void" series of paintings, I painted my void in order to get closer to it.  With each painting I got closer to it, until finally I entered it.  Now I paint from within the void.  Will you meet me there?
See more paintings at www.laladrona.com
